sequenceDiagram
    participant POTUS as President/SecDef
    participant JSOC as Joint Special Operations Command
    participant NSWC as NSW Command
    participant TEAM as SEAL Team Commander
    participant PLAT as Platoon Commander
    participant SQUAD as Squad Leader
    participant OPS as Operators on Ground

    POTUS->>JSOC: Mission Authorization
    JSOC->>NSWC: Tasking Order
    NSWC->>TEAM: Operation Assignment
    TEAM->>PLAT: Mission Brief & Orders
    PLAT->>SQUAD: Tactical Plan
    SQUAD->>OPS: Execution Orders
    
    OPS->>SQUAD: SITREP (Situation Report)
    SQUAD->>PLAT: Status Update
    PLAT->>TEAM: Progress Report
    TEAM->>NSWC: Mission Status
    NSWC->>JSOC: Intel & Updates
    JSOC->>POTUS: Mission Report